description:
Merry christmas to all! And to all a good night...
None of this would be possible... if it werent for Sonic underground... its hard to believe that its already so close to 2014. Net video my fans... will be the NEW YEARS look back!!!

replies.text:
Actually, we don't know for sure if Uncle Chuck is their real uncle. In the show, he is actually portrayed as being Sonic's adoptive fathers brother, and not related to Queen Aleena at all. You gotta understand Sonic Underground is not like the other sonic cartoons in the fact that it's actually unique. yes, Uncle Chuck does look a lot like he's related, but there's the possibility that he just isn't. I believe it's entirely up to the viewer

And no, if he is Sonic manic and sonia's real uncle, he wouldn't be queen aleena's brother in law. They would legitimately be brother and sister
